<!DOCTYPE concept PUBLIC "-//OASIS//DTD DITA Concept//EN" "concept.dtd">
<concept id="concept_vcb_sxq_m3c">
    <title>2. High-Level Architecture</title>
    <conbody>
        <p>The system is composed of four major subsystems:</p>
        <ol id="ol_f43_sxq_m3c">
            <li>
                <p>Content Source Layer</p>
            </li>
            <li>
                <p>Ingestion Engine</p>
            </li>
            <li>
                <p>Retrieval &amp; AI Layer</p>
            </li>
            <li>
                <p>Frontend Chat Interface</p>
            </li>
        </ol>
        <pre>                ┌────────────────────────────┐
                │     Markdown Knowledge     │
                │  (Portfolio Documentation) │
                └─────────────┬──────────────┘
                              │
                       Ingestion Engine
                              │
                      Chunk Generation
                              │
                     Embedding Generation
                              │
                     Vector Index (FAISS)
                              │
                     Retrieval Pipeline
                              │
                        LLM Completion
                              │
                        Chat Interface</pre>
        <p>The architecture separates <b>offline indexing</b> from <b>runtime retrieval</b>.</p>
        <section id="section_mnl_qts_n3c">
            <title>Offline Processing</title>
            <p>Performed by the ingestion engine:</p>
            <ul id="ul_bz4_rts_n3c">
                <li>
                    <p>parse Markdown documents</p>
                </li>
                <li>
                    <p>extract metadata</p>
                </li>
                <li>
                    <p>generate content chunks</p>
                </li>
                <li>
                    <p>compute embeddings</p>
                </li>
                <li>
                    <p>build the vector index</p>
                </li>
            </ul>
        </section>
        <section id="section_fjf_tts_n3c">
            <title>Runtime Processing</title>
            <p>Performed during a user query:</p>
            <ul id="ul_ef3_5ts_n3c">
                <li>
                    <p>query embedding</p>
                </li>
                <li>
                    <p>hybrid retrieval</p>
                </li>
                <li>
                    <p>diversity filtering</p>
                </li>
                <li>
                    <p>semantic reranking</p>
                </li>
                <li>
                    <p>prompt construction</p>
                </li>
                <li>
                    <p>LLM response generation</p>
                </li>
            </ul>
        </section>
    </conbody>
</concept>
